description:
In this episode, we provide an in-depth explanation of materials and textures, guiding you through the process of creating and manipulating them. We learn how to create simple materials, and controlling base color,  roughness, metallic, emission and specular . We will also teach you the concept of Material Instances and Parameters for dynamic material tweaking.
